description: Deletes a what-if analysis created using the  CreateWhatIfAnalysis operation. You can delete only what-if analyses that have a status of ACTIVE or CREATE_FAILED. To get the status, use the  DescribeWhatIfAnalysis operation. You can't delete a what-if analysis while any of its forecasts are being exported.

parameters.name: WhatIfAnalysisArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the what-if analysis that you want to delete.
